      "date": "2014-10-12 06:52:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPlease don't resubmit a patch that failed testing without marking each of the test failures in Maloo against some bug. Otherwise, we are never going to get our testing to pass consistently if everyone ignores the intermittent test failures and resubmits patches until they pass.\n\nIn particular, patches like this should pay close attention to the test failures to avoid potentially enabling a test that is only passing intermittently.",
